Each candle is hand-poured in small batches into a pint sized mason jar in Lancaster, PA. Our vegan dye free soy wax burns at a cooler temperature and slower. This allows an extended clean burn at a slower rate, releasing the captivating scent at a more leisurely pace, and giving the candle a long-lasting experience of up to 84 hours of strong scent throw. Handcrafted and hand painted wooden Fall garden gnome.  Amish made in Lancaster County, PA.   Slight imperfections in the wood and painting due to the handmade nature.  These are not finely painted and are front finished only.  Great porch sitter or garden decor.  Wooden garden gnome measures approximately 19.5" Tall x 12" wide including hat span (garden gnome body is approx. 6" wide) x 1" thick.  Great addition to your fall decor!  Note: Decor on hat could vary depending upon availability.
